# 💼 Sales Performance Dashboard (Excel)

## 📌 Objective
Create an Excel dashboard to track sales by region, customer, and product.

## 🧰 Tools Used
Microsoft Excel

## 📊 Dataset
Sales orders, customers, and product data from internal records

## 🛠️ Methodology
- Structured multiple sheets (orders, customers, products)
- Used VLOOKUP and pivot tables to merge and analyze data
- Created slicers and bar charts for dynamic filtering

## 🔍 Key Insights
- Top 5 customers made up 45% of total sales
- Country B contributed the highest share in Q4
- Category B products outperformed others consistently

📂 File: `Richard Excel Portfolio.xlsx`
